experience

2015-2016

I started the journey towards web developemnt when I was enrolled in UET Lahore. I was enrolled in Electrical Engineering programme. UET is one of the best institue in Pakistan for engineering degree. I started the basic HTML and CSS structures as soon as I was enrolled in university.

{/* - */}

2016-2017

It's been one year since I started my joueney towards programming and development. I have learned the C language and Pythin in one year. I also joined the IET EE On Campus community to grow the basic knowledge of the programming and embedded systems.

{/* - */}

2017-2018

Halfway throught the engineering, this was the best year where I studied the Python, Java OOP and Data Structures. This was going to be the foundation of the start that I was going to take in the next year.

{/* - */}

2018-2019

Landed on my first project based on the front-end design of an eCommerce store. This was the year when I learned the MATLAB and network transmissions. Journey towards a full time eCommerce front-end developer is started

{/* - */}

2019-2020

Started working with the local start up to build solutions for IOT. I worked on multiple projects to build the front-ends of the websites and backend links. In this startup, at the end , I moved completely to the front-end and direction was set. Shopify development is at its peek. Final project at university is also going at rapid pace. Loved the momentum of things until Coivd-19 strike. Due to covid, I got a window to work more exclusively on my skills and keep building on shopify and ReactJS

{/* - */}

2020-2021

First shopify App is in final stages. Shopify development suing the shopify 2.0 features is running at rapid pace. Worked with international companies but left them to create a Saas product of my own. (Continued...)
